h2.heading.heading--secondary#progressbar Progressbar

p.paragraph.
   A progressbar is used for activities that might take more than just a few moments to complete. It has the ability to give quantitative feedback to the user (e.g. 20% uploaded  or 10 of 15 pictures deleted).
   
